        "message": "Patch Set 4:\n\nThanks Max really appreciate you taking on this. please let me know if you have any questions or clarification. I believe the best way to tackle this is like you suggested pull this patch and create a new change on top of this one.\n\nMax Benjamin\n10:33 AM\n↩\nPatch Set 7: -Code-Review\nI'm going to start looking at this today. I'm not sure the best way to communicate changes on top of these changes. I'd like to treat this more like a branch and make another code-review back to it. Maybe I'll make another change-id.",
